queries.sql: SELECT `logbooks`.*, `accounts`.`cust_industry` as `customer`, `logbooks`.`created_at` as `created_at`, `categories`.`name` as `category`, `issues`.`name` as `issue`, `sub_types`.`name` as `sub_type`, `descriptions`.`name` as `description`, `impacts`.`name` as `impact`, `username` FROM `logbooks` JOIN `users` ON `logbooks`.`user_id` = `users`.`id` JOIN `accounts` ON `logbooks`.`account_id` = `accounts`.`id` JOIN `categories` ON `logbooks`.`category_id` = `categories`.`id` JOIN `issues` ON `logbooks`.`issue_id` = `issues`.`id` JOIN `sub_types` ON `logbooks`.`sub_type_id` = `sub_types`.`id` JOIN `descriptions` ON `logbooks`.`description_id` = `descriptions`.`id` JOIN `impacts` ON `logbooks`.`impact_id` = `impacts`.`id` WHERE `logbooks`.`created_at` >= '2024-02-19' AND `logbooks`.`created_at` <= '2024-02-27' ORDER BY `logbooks`.`created_at` DESC
